{"tid":253214,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得用普通數學讀物理好難？","createTime":"2017-05-22T08:22:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T09:03:16.000Z","uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"064ef575e6e54275282c4edce6ed39bcbf96f0d1","tid":253214,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:22:31.000Z","msg":"咩均加速方程 v = u + at, v^2 - u^2 = 2as, s = ut + 0.5at^2<br />\n<br />\n其實 v = / -g dt = -gt + C<br />\ns = / v dt = / -gt + C dt = Ct - 0.5gt^2 + D<br />\n<br />\n再 sub boundary condition 搵埋 d constant <br />\n<br />\n然後 g vector 應該係 -9.81j，u and v 全部用哂 vector 黎做先係最輕鬆簡單 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18e41812acb7773b7a83511f4e4602900a68832","tid":253214,"uid":53278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:43:33.000Z","msg":"咁個t呢"},{"pid":"397861da5962ed4afb7f5ce74b1356a5d30f0d14","tid":253214,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T09:03:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁個t呢</blockquote><br />\n求其做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}